"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?41/58/42915?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Chronic rhinosinusitis (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?39/44/40643?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: The common cold in children (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?16/18/16674?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Rinsing out your nose with salt water (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
